snippet: After a forgettable rookie year, the former first-round draft pick Prince Amukamara is being treated less delicately by the team.
abstract: Development of New York Giants defensive back Prince Amukamara, the former first-round draft pick, is being treated less delicately by the Giants after his forgettable rookie year.
lead_paragraph: After a forgettable rookie year, the former first-round draft pick Prince Amukamara is being treated less delicately by the team.
